OL,3,C'Strong smell of petrol' as NRW
OL,4,Cinvestigates fuel pollution incident
OL,6,FNatural Resources Wales says it's
OL,7,Fconducting an investigation into a
OL,8,Ffuel pollution incident in
OL,9,FPontygwindy, Caerphilly.
OL,11,FIt's after local residents complained
OL,12,Fof a strong smell of petrol in the
OL,13,Farea.
OL,15,FAt present the source of the pollution
OL,16,Fappears to be near Howard Drive, Dyfed
OL,17,FDrive and Davies Drive in the
OL,18,FChurchill Park area.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/3
